cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a method for visual classification tasks, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of a discriminative structured analysis dictionary and a simple classifier also indicates that it may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The mention of large-scale datasets and distributed learning suggests that it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
